```python
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split

data = df.sample(n=10000, random_state=1025)
x = data.drop(columns=['Time','Class'])
y = data[['Class']]

X_train, X_valid, y_train, y_valid = train_test_split(x,y, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)
print(X_train.shape, X_valid.shape, y_train.shape, y_valid.shape)
```

<pre>
(8000, 29) (2000, 29) (8000, 1) (2000, 1)
</pre>
정규화



```python
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler, StandardScaler, RobustScaler

scaler = MinMaxScaler()
X_train = scaler.fit_transform(X_train)
X_valid = scaler.transform(X_valid)
```


```python
from pyod.utils.example import visualize
from pyod.utils.data import evaluate_print
from pyod.utils.data import generate_data
from pyod.models.knn import KNN
from pyod.models.lof import LOF
from pyod.models.hbos import HBOS
from pyod.models.pca import PCA
from pyod.models.iforest import IForest
from pyod.models.ecod import ECOD

from sklearn.metrics import *
```


```python
# setting parameters
random_state = np.random.RandomState(1025)
outliers_fraction = 0.0014
# Define seven outlier detection tools to be compared
classifiers = {
        'KNN': KNN(contamination=outliers_fraction),
        'LOF': LOF(contamination=outliers_fraction),
        'HBOS': HBOS(contamination=outliers_fraction),
        'PCA': PCA(contamination=outliers_fraction),
        'Isolation Forest': IForest(contamination=outliers_fraction,random_state=random_state),
}

# model fitting
for i, (clf_name, clf) in enumerate(classifiers.items()):
    clf.fit(X_train)
    y_pred = clf.labels_
    print(clf_name)
    print('accuracy : ',round(accuracy_score(y_train,y_pred),3))
    print('precision : ',round(precision_score(y_train,y_pred),3))
    print('recall : ',round(recall_score(y_train,y_pred),3))
    print('f1 : ',round(f1_score(y_train,y_pred),3))
    print()
    y_test_pred = clf.predict(X_valid)
    y_test_scores = clf.decision_function(X_valid)
    print('test accuracy : ',round(accuracy_score(y_valid,y_test_pred),3))
    print('test precision : ',round(precision_score(y_valid,y_test_pred),3))
    print('test recall : ',round(recall_score(y_valid,y_test_pred),3))
    print('test f1 : ',round(f1_score(y_valid,y_test_pred),3))
    
    print('-------------------')
    
    
    
```

```python

```


```python
classifiers = {
        'DeepSVDD': DeepSVDD(),
        'ECOD': ECOD(),
}

# model fitting
for i, (clf_name, clf) in enumerate(classifiers.items()):
    clf.fit(X_train)
    y_pred = clf.labels_
    print(clf_name)
    y_val_pred = clf.predict(X_val)
    y_val_scores = clf.decision_function(X_val)
    print(clf_name)
    print('accuracy : ',round(accuracy_score(y_val,y_val_pred),3))
    print('precision : ',round(precision_score(y_val,y_val_pred),3))
    print('recall : ',round(recall_score(y_val,y_val_pred),3))
    print('f1 : ',round(f1_score(y_val,y_val_pred),3))
    
    y_test_pred = clf.predict(X_test)
    y_test_scores = clf.decision_function(X_test)
    print(clf_name)
    print('accuracy : ',round(accuracy_score(y_test,y_test_pred),3))
    print('precision : ',round(precision_score(y_test,y_test_pred),3))
    print('recall : ',round(recall_score(y_test,y_test_pred),3))
    print('f1 : ',round(f1_score(y_test,y_test_pred),3))

print('-------------------')
```
